      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI (hemolysis index) must be directly mapped to the clinical endpoint (plasma-free hemoglobin threshold) with documented traceability at Gradation 3.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is computed from shear-stress exposure integral but traceability to the clinical plasma-free hemoglobin threshold is only partially documented. Achieved Gradation 2."
