      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty for the power-law hemolysis damage model must be quantified against alternative constitutive relationships at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty was not assessed. Only the Giersiepen power-law model was used; no comparison to alternative hemolysis models (e.g., strain-based) was performed. Critical gap at MRL 5."
